Nginx Server Block Configuration:

Run the following commands:

sudo tee /etc/nginx/sites-available/larafony > /dev/null <<'EOF'
server {
    listen 80;
    server_name larafony.local;
    root {{DOC_ROOT}};

    index index.php;

    location / {
        try_files $uri $uri/ /index.php?$query_string;
    }

    location ~ \.php$ {
        fastcgi_pass unix:/var/run/php/php8.5-fpm.sock;
        fastcgi_index index.php;
        fastcgi_param SCRIPT_FILENAME $realpath_root$fastcgi_script_name;
        include fastcgi_params;
    }
}
EOF

sudo ln -s /etc/nginx/sites-available/larafony /etc/nginx/sites-enabled/
sudo systemctl reload nginx

Add to /etc/hosts:
echo "127.0.0.1 larafony.local" | sudo tee -a /etc/hosts

Then visit: http://larafony.local/notes
